            Undergraduate Studies
          
The Department of Communication provides undergraduate students with a broad liberal education that covers communication from the personal through the international levels and builds responsible citizenship






            Graduate Studies
          
The Department of Communication offers a wide ranging directory of useful information for current and prospective graduate students.






            Graduate FAQ
          
Frequently asked questions on graduate issues such as: "How do I pay for this? How are your programs structured?"






            Undergraduate Advising and Registration
          
LAS Advising can assist students with declaring the major and minor, and planning an appropriate course of study.










